  "reviews": [
    {
      "author": "FionaE-91",
      "text": "Waring Interiors revamped our house, making it stylish, elegant and a flexible canvas for individuals to make rooms their own. Ashley has an eye for colours that work and is able to see real potential in tired spaces. Waring Interiors partnered with talented trades who worked at speed which allowed us to refurbish the house within a tight timescale.",
      "role": "Customer"
    },
    {
      "author": "MichelleZ-6",
      "text": "Ashley has great taste! She can certainly dress the most beautiful bed with comfort and class. Thank you",
      "role": "Customer"
    },
    {
      "author": "EmilyK-192",
      "text": "Ashley is creative, hard working, attentive to detail and works seamlessly with her clients. I would highly recommend her.",
      "role": "Customer"
    },
    {
      "author": "BibaL",
      "text": "Great to work with, always available, fantastic ideas put into reality. Saved me money and transformed the downstairs of my house!",
      "role": "Customer"
    },
    {
      "author": "AndrewN-500",
      "text": "Amazing service which was helpful, imaginative and brought classical elegant style to my home. I am so grateful for Ashley's dedicated and personal touch in making house a home. Cannot recommend more highly. Effortless process which made it all so enjoyable.",
      "role": "Customer"
    }
